  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to determine the long-term effect and security of the surgical&#xD;
      treatment and observation only on ocular alignment, binocular stereopsis, and quality of life&#xD;
      in children with moderate intermittent exotropia.&#xD;
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
